Package: quone
Title: R Companion for the Quone Language
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    person("Quone", "Language Project", email = "noreply@quone-lang.org",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description:
    Developer-experience tools for working with the Quone language from R.
    Discovers and invokes the 'quonec' compiler, scaffolds projects, runs
    a watch-and-rebuild loop, surfaces compiler diagnostics in RStudio
    and Positron, rewrites R-side runtime tracebacks back to '.Q' source
    via compiler-emitted source maps, registers a 'knitr' / Quarto
    engine for Quone code chunks, wraps the real 'quonec repl', wraps
    the real 'quonec fmt', and installs the real 'quonec lsp' Language
    Server into popular editors. The package is for authors of Quone,
    not a runtime dependency of the R that 'quonec' generates.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/quone-lang/quone
BugReports: https://github.com/quone-lang/quone/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
